data.description: seller is replumbing house prior to closing. Beautiful 3 bed 2 bath pool home located in the highly sought after community of Valencia Place in Orlando. As you enter this home, you’re greeted by open concept floor plan which has the kitchen overlooking the living room and pool area. The kitchen features granite counters, upgraded cabinets, and breakfast bar. The living room is oversized and connects directly to a dining space and all while overlooking the patio and pool area. The Master Bedroom is large and features a walk-in closet along with an ensuite bathroom with dual vanities and walk in shower. The guest bedrooms are both well-appointed and share a guest bathroom located on the other side of this split plan. The outdoor space is fantastic as this home has both a covered and uncovered area perfect for any occasion. As a bonus, the covered patio boasts a hammock perfect for relaxing poolside on a hot summer day. This home also features a roof installed in 2016 as well as water filtration system installed in 2017. If that wasn’t enough, this home is located within minutes of UCF, Valencia College as well as countless dining, shopping, and entertainment options as well as proximity to major highways like SR 417 & 408. If you’re looking for a turnkey pool home in the Orlando area, then look no further because you’re home!
